overview: Alyssa Reece is an experienced sex therapist and when it comes to hearing the stories of her clients… she can’t get enough. So sit back, relax and get ready to embark on the sexy tales Alyssa’s friends have to offer in Private Specials, Off Duty Therapist and experience some the hottest Private action yet! There’s Eveline Dellai, a stunning brunette who’s in for a night of passion after being seduced at the park; Sharon White, a horny girl who takes care of a lucky waiter with some extra special sex treatment after a nasty fall; Subil Arch, a saucy blonde who’s client turns up with his flies already open; and what for Alyssa herself? Watch as she creates her very own sex story right here in Private Specials, Off Duty Therapist.
title: Off Duty Therapist
